    (H.comap (QuotientGroup.mk' (Subgroup.center (Matrix.SpecialLinearGroup (Fin 2) F))))
    (by rw [H.index_comap_of_surjective hsurj]; exact hidx)
  rw [‚Üź Subgroup.map_comap_eq_self_of_surjective hsurj H, htop,
    Subgroup.map_top_of_surjective _ hsurj]

/-- **The cardinality of `PSL‚āā` of a finite char-3 field** (PROVEN
2026-07-22): `|PSL‚āā(F)| ¬∑ 2 = q(q¬≤ ‚ąí 1)`, from the vendored
