/-- **The five exceptional Dickson groups: subgroups of index `‚Č§ 2`
are even of order `‚Č• 12`** (PROVEN 2026-07-22): in `A‚āĄ`, `A‚āÖ` and
`PSL‚āā(ūĚĒĹ_{3^m})` an index-`‚Č§ 2` subgroup is the whole group (generation
