`Gal(K/‚Ąö) ‚ČÉ őď ‚Ąö / ker u ‚ČÉ u.range`, recorded by
`K.fixingSubgroup = u.ker` and `[K : ‚Ąö] = #u.range`. Intended proof
(pure infinite-Galois bookkeeping, as in
`open_normal_subgroup_eq_top_of_inertia_le`): `ker ŌĀ ‚Č§ ker u` (`hu`
