/-- **The quantitative local-to-global inertia transport** (PROVEN
2026-07-23 ‚ÄĒ the strengthening of `MazurTorsion`'s
`exists_prime_over_inertia_eq_bot_of_le_fixingSubgroup` from
"image trivial ‚áí inertia trivial" to "inertia order divides the image
order"): for a Galois number field `K = (ker u)^fix` and a prime `Q`
of `ūĚďě K` over `q`, the order of the ideal-inertia subgroup of
`Gal(K/‚Ąö)` at `Q` divides any multiple `n` of the order of the image
under `u` of the local inertia at `q`. Immediate from the general
transport theorem `inertia_card_dvd_of_card_map_localInertiaGroup_dvd`
of `Fermat.FLT.FreyCurve.InertiaCardTransport` (proven there with `u`
an arbitrary group homomorphism cutting out `K`): the restriction
`ŌÄ : őď ‚Ąö ‚Üí Gal(K/‚Ąö)` has kernel `K.fixingSubgroup = ker u`, so
`#ŌÄ(I_q) = #u(I_q)`; the fixed field `K'` of `H := ŌÄ(I_q)` is fixed
pointwise by `I_q`, so the Minkowski embedding gives a prime of
`ūĚďě K'` over `q` of ramification index `1`; a prime `Q‚āÄ` of `ūĚďě K`
above it then has `e(Q‚āÄ|q) = e(Q‚āÄ|Q‚āÄ') = #I_{Gal(K/K')}(Q‚āÄ) ‚ą£
#Gal(K/K') = #H` (tower multiplicativity plus Lagrange), and
prime-independence of the inertia order in the Galois extension `K/‚Ąö`
(`Ideal.card_inertia_eq_ramificationIdxIn`) moves the bound to `Q`. -/
theorem inertia_card_dvd_of_map_localInertiaGroup_card_dvd
    (K : IntermediateField ‚Ąö (AlgebraicClosure ‚Ąö)) [NumberField K]
    [IsGalois ‚Ąö K]
    (u : őď ‚Ąö ‚Üí* GL (Fin 2) (Dickson.K 3))
    (hfix : K.fixingSubgroup = u.ker)
    {q : ‚Ąē} (hq : q.Prime)
    (Q : Ideal (NumberField.RingOfIntegers K)) (hQ : Q.IsPrime)
    (hmem : ((q : ‚Ąē) : NumberField.RingOfIntegers K) ‚ąą Q)
    (n : ‚Ąē)
    (hn : Nat.card (Subgroup.map u
      (Subgroup.map (Field.absoluteGaloisGroup.map (algebraMap ‚Ąö
        (IsDedekindDomain.HeightOneSpectrum.adicCompletion ‚Ąö
          hq.toHeightOneSpectrumRingOfIntegersRat))).toMonoidHom
        (localInertiaGroup hq.toHeightOneSpectrumRingOfIntegersRat))) ‚ą£ n) :
    Nat.card (Q.inertia (K ‚ČÉ‚āź[‚Ąö] K)) ‚ą£ n :=
  inertia_card_dvd_of_card_map_localInertiaGroup_dvd K u hfix hq Q hQ hmem n hn

