ring `IC-N`; its image under `integralClosureInclusion` ‚ÄĒ which equals
`ŌÉ ‚ÄĘ xŐā ‚ąí xŐā` by `AlgEquiv.restrictNormal_commutes` ‚ÄĒ would then be a
