i.e. the Mellin transform (2) of G. Poitou, *Sur les petits
discriminants*, S√©m. Delange‚ÄďPisot‚ÄďPoitou 18 (1976/77), exp. 6, at the
test function `F = f/cosh(x/2)` of its Proposition 5.  Since `f` is
