ideals `ūĚĒ≠` of `ūĚí™_K`, with `f = odlyzkoTestFn` ‚ÄĒ the ultrametric term
`(4/n)¬∑ő£_{ūĚĒ≠,m} ‚Ä¶` of inequality (8) of Poitou (exp. 6, p. 6-08)
