* the `őõ‚āÄ`-level functional equation pairing `C` with
  `[ūĚĒ°]C‚ĀĽ¬Ļ = dedekindDualClass K C` (from
  `WeakFEPair.functional_equation‚āÄ` at `őĶ = 1` once `(P C).symm` is
