`LSeriesSummable_of_sum_norm_bigO`), and the convolution identity
`(ő£_{ūĚĒü ‚ą£ ūĚĒě} őľ_K(ūĚĒü)) = [ūĚĒě = 1]` yields `ő∂_K(s)¬∑L(b, s) = 1`, so
`ő∂_K(s) ‚Č† 0`. -/
