constant `m = exp(‚ąí(3/2)¬∑ő£_ūĚĒ≠ NūĚĒ≠^{‚ąí2})` ‚ÄĒ the `ő∂(2ŌÉ)/ő∂(ŌÉ)`-style
constant of the classical estimate, uniform in `im s`. -/
theorem dedekindZeta_norm_lower_of_re_eq_two (K : Type*) [Field K]
    [NumberField K] :
    ‚ąÉ m : ‚ĄĚ, 0 < m ‚ąß ‚ąÄ s : ‚Ąā, s.re = 2 ‚Üí
      m ‚Č§ ‚ÄĖNumberField.dedekindZeta K s‚ÄĖ := by
