of conjugation on `f` is a `MonoidHom` `őł' : őď ‚Ąö ‚Üí* ‚Ą§/2` (the four
sign-composition cases are proven by explicit rewriting), surjective
via `p`, trivial on `ker ŌĀ` (`u g = 1` there), and elements of
