  ¬∑ exact serre_elimination_arith V hV hŌĀ habs b e u hu ŌÄ hŌÄ (Or.inr (Or.inl h))
  ¬∑ exact serre_elimination_arith V hV hŌĀ habs b e u hu ŌÄ hŌÄ
      (Or.inr (Or.inr (Or.inl h)))
  ¬∑ exact serre_elimination_arith V hV hŌĀ habs b e u hu ŌÄ hŌÄ
