‚ÄĒ evaluated at `n = 6` against the WORST signature (totally complex,
`2r‚āā ‚Č§ 6`, and `4/ŌÄ > 1`), where it reads
`|d_K| ‚Č• 6¬Ļ¬≤¬∑ŌÄ‚Ā∂/(4‚Ā∂¬∑720¬≤) = 985.3‚Ä¶`, already with the crude `ŌÄ > 3`:
`6¬Ļ¬≤¬∑3‚Ā∂ = 1586874322944 > 432¬∑4‚Ā∂¬∑720¬≤ = 917294284800`. Note `432` is
