/-- **The stable line with locally-unramified quotient character at
`2` and `3`** (DERIVED 2026-07-18 from the at-`3` Serre-swap leaf and
the at-`2` tame bookkeeping leaf): a reducible mod-3 hardly ramified
representation has a stable LINE whose quotient character is unramified
at `2` AND at `3`. The at-`3` leaf provides the line and its at-`3`
unramifiedness; the at-`2` leaf applies to any stable line. -/
theorem exists_line_with_locally_unramified_quotCharacter
    {k : Type u} [Finite k] [Field k] [Algebra ‚Ą§_[3] k]
    [TopologicalSpace k] [DiscreteTopology k]
    (V : Type*) [AddCommGroup V] [Module k V] [Module.Finite k V]
    [Module.Free k V]
    (hV : Module.rank k V = 2) {ŌĀ : GaloisRep ‚Ąö k V}
    (hŌĀ : IsHardlyRamified (show Odd 3 by decide) hV ŌĀ)
    (W‚āÄ : Submodule k V) (hW‚āÄ0 : W‚āÄ ‚Č† ‚ä•) (hW‚āÄtop : W‚āÄ ‚Č† ‚ä§)
    (hW‚āÄstable : ‚ąÄ g : őď ‚Ąö, W‚āÄ.map (ŌĀ g) ‚Č§ W‚āÄ) :
    ‚ąÉ (W : Submodule k V) (Ōá‚āā : őď ‚Ąö ‚Üí* kň£),
      Module.finrank k W = 1 ‚ąß
      (‚ąÄ g v, v ‚ąą W ‚Üí ŌĀ g v ‚ąą W) ‚ąß
      (‚ąÄ g v, W.mkQ (ŌĀ g v) = (Ōá‚āā g : k) ‚ÄĘ W.mkQ v) ‚ąß
      (localInertiaGroup Nat.prime_two.toHeightOneSpectrumRingOfIntegersRat ‚Č§
        (Ōá‚āā.comp (Field.absoluteGaloisGroup.map (algebraMap ‚Ąö
          (IsDedekindDomain.HeightOneSpectrum.adicCompletion ‚Ąö
            Nat.prime_two.toHeightOneSpectrumRingOfIntegersRat))).toMonoidHom).ker) ‚ąß
      (localInertiaGroup
          Nat.prime_three.toHeightOneSpectrumRingOfIntegersRat ‚Č§
        (Ōá‚āā.comp (Field.absoluteGaloisGroup.map (algebraMap ‚Ąö
          (IsDedekindDomain.HeightOneSpectrum.adicCompletion ‚Ąö
            Nat.prime_three.toHeightOneSpectrumRingOfIntegersRat))).toMonoidHom).ker) := by
  obtain ‚ü®W, Ōá‚āā, hWfr, hWstable, hŌá‚āā, h3‚ü© :=
    exists_line_with_unramified_quotCharacter_at_three V hV hŌĀ
      W‚āÄ hW‚āÄ0 hW‚āÄtop hW‚āÄstable
  exact ‚ü®W, Ōá‚āā, hWfr, hWstable, hŌá‚āā,
    quotCharacter_unramified_at_two V hV hŌĀ W Ōá‚āā hWfr hWstable hŌá‚āā, h3‚ü©

